all visitors are welcome.

00:05:56.023 --> 00:05:57.592 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:05:57.625 --> 00:06:00.194 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Footsteps approaching ]

00:06:00.228 --> 00:06:05.733 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:06:05.766 --> 00:06:08.035 position:13% line:89% align:start
I am Headon...

00:06:08.069 --> 00:06:10.403 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Gasping ]

00:06:10.437 --> 00:06:13.140 position:10% line:83% align:start
...the caretaker
of this tower.

00:06:13.174 --> 00:06:14.609 position:52% line:89% align:start
[ Shouts ]

00:06:16.110 --> 00:06:17.712 position:58% line:89% align:start
Tower?

00:06:22.116 --> 00:06:23.651 position:64% line:89% align:start
Mm.

00:06:23.684 --> 00:06:25.019 position:58% line:89% align:start
Tower?

00:06:25.052 --> 00:06:26.721 position:41% line:89% align:start
This is it? Really?

00:06:26.754 --> 00:06:31.025 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's a pleasure to meet you,
my dear Master Bam.

00:06:31.058 --> 00:06:32.360 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:06:32.392 --> 00:06:34.427 position:47% line:83% align:start
Wait a minute.
How do you know my name?

00:06:34.461 --> 00:06:35.930 position:44% line:89% align:start
You saw Rachel?!

00:06:35.963 --> 00:06:37.430 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:06:38.398 --> 00:06:40.334 position:38% line:89% align:start
You talked with her?

00:06:40.368 --> 00:06:41.569 position:38% line:89% align:start
I followed her here.

00:06:41.602 --> 00:06:43.436 position:41% line:83% align:start
I was trying to get
to th--

00:06:43.470 --> 00:06:47.775 position:5% line:83% align:start
The answer can always be found
at the top of the tower.

00:06:47.808 --> 00:06:49.310 position:52% line:89% align:start
At the top?

00:06:49.343 --> 00:06:51.212 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:06:51.245 --> 00:06:53.446 position:44% line:89% align:start
Top of the tower.

00:06:55.082 --> 00:06:56.483 position:41% line:89% align:start
She went up there.

00:06:56.517 --> 00:06:58.619 position:5% line:89% align:start
Will you take the test?

00:06:58.653 --> 00:07:01.589 position:10% line:83% align:start
The one required
to climb the tower.

00:07:01.622 --> 00:07:03.724 position:41% line:89% align:start
What kind of test?

00:07:05.760 --> 00:07:06.928 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:07:06.961 --> 00:07:13.734 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:13.768 --> 00:07:20.473 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:07:20.508 --> 00:07:23.144 position:35% line:89% align:start
The rules are simple.

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:28.416 position:27% line:89% align:start
You will enter the cage.

00:07:28.448 --> 00:07:29.784 position:35% line:89% align:start
If you break the ball

00:07:29.817 --> 00:07:32.219 position:47% line:83% align:start
while avoiding
the White Steel Eel,

00:07:32.253 --> 00:07:33.955 position:41% line:89% align:start
you pass the test.

00:07:33.988 --> 00:07:35.256 position:44% line:89% align:start
Will you take it?

00:07:35.289 --> 00:07:36.991 position:24% line:89% align:start
If you wish to turn back,

00:07:37.024 --> 00:07:38.359 position:44% line:89% align:start
now is the time.

00:07:38.392 --> 00:07:40.094 position:30% line:89% align:start
The tower is dangerous.

00:07:40.127 --> 00:07:41.529 position:35% line:89% align:start
For someone like you,

00:07:41.562 --> 00:07:43.631 position:64% line:77% align:start
death is...
[ Bam panting ]

00:07:44.131 --> 00:07:45.433 position:64% line:89% align:start
Mm?

00:07:45.465 --> 00:07:47.068 position:52% line:89% align:start
Marvelous.

00:07:48.402 --> 00:07:49.670 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:07:56.143 --> 00:07:58.112 position:47% line:89% align:start
Mm.

00:07:58.145 --> 00:07:59.914 position:16% line:89% align:start
[ Stammers ]

00:08:01.716 --> 00:08:03.517 position:10% line:89% align:start
[ Speaking foreign language ]

00:08:03.551 --> 00:08:05.252 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:08:05.286 --> 00:08:14.695 position:52% line:83% align:start
[ Shouting
in foreign language ]

00:08:17.431 --> 00:08:19.200 position:19% line:89% align:start
[ Gasping ]

00:08:20.835 --> 00:08:23.471 position:13% line:77% align:start
[ Grunts ]
[ Electricity zapping ]

00:08:23.504 --> 00:08:25.539 position:44% line:83% align:start
You understand us
now, right?

00:08:25.573 --> 00:08:27.475 position:13% line:89% align:start
Uh, yeah.

00:08:27.508 --> 00:08:29.577 position:13% line:83% align:start
That high quality pocket's
too good for you.

00:08:29.610 --> 00:08:31.812 position:21% line:77% align:start
You don't deserve it.
Pocket?

00:08:31.846 --> 00:08:35.082 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's not just a translator,
it's also our lifeline

00:08:35.116 --> 00:08:36.550 position:50% line:89% align:start
in the tower.

00:08:36.584 --> 00:08:39.220 position:30% line:83% align:start
Face toward it and then
say, "invisible mode."

00:08:39.253 --> 00:08:41.288 position:7% line:89% align:start
Um, invisible mode.

00:08:41.322 --> 00:08:43.724 position:16% line:77% align:start
[ Gasps ]
Don't look so shocked.

00:08:43.758 --> 00:08:45.626 position:33% line:83% align:start
By the way, if you say
"visible mode,"

00:08:45.659 --> 00:08:47.194 position:44% line:71% align:start
it'll revert to --
I knew you were
an irregular

00:08:47.228 --> 00:08:48.462 position:24% line:89% align:start
right off the bat.

00:08:48.496 --> 00:08:49.964 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm not sure I know
what an irregular --

00:08:49.997 --> 00:08:51.966 position:44% line:83% align:start
They're outsiders
who manage to enter the tower

00:08:51.999 --> 00:08:54.301 position:38% line:83% align:start
by opening the gates
on their own.

00:08:54.335 --> 00:08:55.870 position:55% line:83% align:start
Whatever.
But you look kind of weak

00:08:55.903 --> 00:08:57.972 position:24% line:83% align:start
to be an irregular.
-I don't get it.

00:08:58.005 --> 00:09:00.574 position:19% line:83% align:start
Why are we getting involved
with an irregular, anyway?

00:09:00.608 --> 00:09:02.443 position:5% line:83% align:start
Are you trying to say
that you could care less

00:09:02.476 --> 00:09:03.611 position:5% line:89% align:start
if the White Steel Eel

00:09:03.644 --> 00:09:05.112 position:5% line:83% align:start
turns him into sushi
for breakfast?

00:09:05.146 --> 00:09:07.581 position:24% line:83% align:start
Headon: You may be
Yuri, Princess of Jahad,

00:09:07.615 --> 00:09:09.316 position:30% line:83% align:start
but if the king
were to learn of this,

00:09:09.350 --> 00:09:11.085 position:19% line:89% align:start
you would be executed.

00:09:11.118 --> 00:09:12.453 position:35% line:89% align:start
Am I wrong?

00:09:12.486 --> 00:09:13.921 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:09:15.389 --> 00:09:17.758 position:30% line:83% align:start
That's only if you blab
to the king.

00:09:17.792 --> 00:09:19.660 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Lady Yuri!
-I devote myself

00:09:19.693 --> 00:09:21.462 position:21% line:83% align:start
to maintaining order
in the tower

00:09:21.495 --> 00:09:24.665 position:33% line:83% align:start
and ensuring
the royal family's prosperity.

00:09:26.634 --> 00:09:29.538 position:33% line:83% align:start
Therefore, I am simply
doing my job.

00:09:29.570 --> 00:09:30.638 position:5% line:77% align:start
Hm.
[ Sighs ]

00:09:30.671 --> 00:09:32.873 position:5% line:83% align:start
Then why give him
an unfair test?

00:09:32.907 --> 00:09:35.009 position:5% line:83% align:start
Even the guys on the 20th floor
have trouble

00:09:35.042 --> 00:09:38.479 position:5% line:83% align:start
dealing with that oversized eel
in the stainless steel tux.

00:09:38.513 --> 00:09:40.047 position:72% line:89% align:start
Unfair?

00:09:40.081 --> 00:09:43.284 position:13% line:83% align:start
May I respectfully remind you
that he's an irregular?

00:09:43.317 --> 00:09:45.920 position:5% line:83% align:start
As a guide, do you sense any
hidden powers within him?

00:09:45.953 --> 00:09:48.622 position:5% line:83% align:start
Could there be any chance
he'll suddenly transform?

00:09:48.656 --> 00:09:50.691 position:44% line:83% align:start
I have to admit,
he seems fairly agile.

00:09:50.724 --> 00:09:52.626 position:5% line:83% align:start
There!
Even Evan says so.

00:09:52.660 --> 00:09:53.961 position:5% line:83% align:start
Although you'll also
have to admit

00:09:53.994 --> 00:09:56.397 position:5% line:77% align:start
how puny and frail
he looks.
[ Chuckles ]

00:09:56.430 --> 00:09:59.967 position:5% line:83% align:start
But if you put my back
against a wall...

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.103 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'd admit he's a bit
handsome.

00:10:02.136 --> 00:10:04.205 position:16% line:83% align:start
Headon, couldn't you drop
the level of his test

00:10:04.238 --> 00:10:06.807 position:21% line:83% align:start
a teensy weensy bit,
just this one time?

00:10:06.841 --> 00:10:09.043 position:5% line:83% align:start
I am caretaker
of the tower.

00:10:09.076 --> 00:10:11.779 position:5% line:83% align:start
It is necessary to determine
if he is worthy of it.

00:10:11.812 --> 00:10:13.914 position:35% line:77% align:start
Yes, but --
I'll be okay.

00:10:13.948 --> 00:10:15.783 position:41% line:83% align:start
-What?!
-I don't know who you are.

00:10:15.816 --> 00:10:18.553 position:10% line:83% align:start
but I appreciate
your consideration.

00:10:18.587 --> 00:10:22.189 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yuri: You don't even recognize
a Princess of Jahad.

00:10:22.223 --> 00:10:24.593 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're actually going to try
to climb the tower

00:10:24.625 --> 00:10:26.293 position:5% line:89% align:start
when you're <i>that</i> ignorant?

00:10:26.327 --> 00:10:27.928 position:5% line:89% align:start
Are you <i>trying</i> to die?

00:10:27.962 --> 00:10:29.830 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's a lot better
than just giving up, isn't it?

00:10:29.864 --> 00:10:32.800 position:5% line:77% align:start
Mm.
If you're so determined
to have him

00:10:32.833 --> 00:10:35.537 position:44% line:83% align:start
climb the tower,
Princess Yuri,

00:10:35.570 --> 00:10:37.404 position:35% line:89% align:start
then why not lend him

00:10:37.438 --> 00:10:39.807 position:50% line:83% align:start
the Black March?
[ Scoffs ]

00:10:39.840 --> 00:10:42.577 position:19% line:83% align:start
Depending on who wields it,
as I'm sure you are aware,

00:10:42.611 --> 00:10:44.211 position:41% line:83% align:start
the legendary sword
of Jahad

00:10:44.245 --> 00:10:47.414 position:5% line:83% align:start
can be a lump of lead or a blade
that cuts through anything.

00:10:47.448 --> 00:10:49.416 position:5% line:5% align:start
Hold on there!
Only a princess of Jahad

00:10:49.450 --> 00:10:50.651 position:13% line:5% align:start
can wield
the Black March!

00:10:50.684 --> 00:10:52.019 position:5% line:5% align:start
Do you have an inkling
of what'd happen

00:10:52.052 --> 00:10:53.522 position:13% line:5% align:start
if word got out
that another wielded its --

00:10:53.555 --> 00:10:55.356 position:30% line:83% align:start
Arms inventory.
Visible mode activated.

00:10:55.389 --> 00:10:56.457 position:19% line:83% align:start
Lady Yuri!
You're not --

00:10:56.490 --> 00:11:02.163 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:02.196 --> 00:11:07.602 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:07.636 --> 00:11:08.836 position:16% line:89% align:start
Listen to me.

00:11:08.869 --> 00:11:11.038 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm going to let you
borrow this for now.

00:11:11.071 --> 00:11:12.406 position:10% line:89% align:start
Lady Yuri!

00:11:13.741 --> 00:11:15.242 position:52% line:83% align:start
But that's
an amazing sword.

00:11:15.276 --> 00:11:18.712 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's right, but do you want
to climb the tower or not?

00:11:18.746 --> 00:11:19.914 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:11:19.947 --> 00:11:27.522 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:27.556 --> 00:11:35.062 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:11:35.095 --> 00:11:36.997 position:5% line:77% align:start
[ Sighs deeply ]
I can't believe

00:11:37.031 --> 00:11:39.266 position:41% line:83% align:start
you really let him
borrow the sword.

00:11:39.300 --> 00:11:41.402 position:5% line:83% align:start
You're the one who told me
to give it to him!

00:11:41.435 --> 00:11:44.004 position:24% line:83% align:start
I promise to give it back
after I break the ball.

00:11:44.038 --> 00:11:45.139 position:21% line:89% align:start
[ Sighs ]

00:11:45.172 --> 00:11:46.874 position:7% line:83% align:start
First, worry about
staying alive,

00:11:46.907 --> 00:11:49.476 position:5% line:83% align:start
then think about the rest,
alright?

00:11:49.511 --> 00:11:51.879 position:58% line:89% align:start
Got it.

00:11:51.912 --> 00:11:55.082 position:33% line:89% align:start
Lady Yuri, honestly...

00:11:55.115 --> 00:11:57.284 position:5% line:83% align:start
have you fallen in love with him
at first sight?

00:11:57.318 --> 00:11:58.852 position:69% line:77% align:start
[ Yelps ]
[ Bones crunch ]

00:11:58.886 --> 00:12:00.555 position:78% line:83% align:start
Aah!
Keep quiet.

00:12:00.589 --> 00:12:03.625 position:21% line:5% align:start
You don't truly believe an
irregular will change the tower.

00:12:03.658 --> 00:12:05.694 position:55% line:5% align:start
That's absurd.
Don't be stupid.

00:12:05.726 --> 00:12:07.696 position:5% line:83% align:start
You know how much I detest
being bored.

00:12:07.728 --> 00:12:09.496 position:21% line:83% align:start
Come on,
that's all this is.

00:12:09.531 --> 00:12:14.301 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:14.335 --> 00:12:18.372 position:21% line:83% align:start
The truth is, there's only
one way to pass this test.

00:12:20.407 --> 00:12:21.408 position:64% line:89% align:start
Mm.

00:12:21.442 --> 00:12:27.682 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:12:27.716 --> 00:12:29.183 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:12:32.486 --> 00:12:34.054 position:19% line:83% align:start
What?!
[ Gasps ]

00:12:35.690 --> 00:12:37.958 position:52% line:83% align:start
That idiot!
What's he doing?!

00:12:38.993 --> 00:12:41.395 position:33% line:83% align:start
Headon: If you provide
any more assistance,

00:12:41.428 --> 00:12:42.597 position:50% line:89% align:start
he will fail.

00:12:42.631 --> 00:12:44.666 position:13% line:83% align:start
Do you want me
to just watch him die?

00:12:44.699 --> 00:12:46.133 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, no!

00:12:51.706 --> 00:12:54.341 position:27% line:89% align:start
It is the path he chose.

00:12:55.876 --> 00:12:57.378 position:7% line:89% align:start
Get out of my way.

00:12:57.411 --> 00:12:59.847 position:7% line:83% align:start
That's not quite the proper way
to address me.

00:12:59.880 --> 00:13:01.949 position:7% line:83% align:start
Shut up! You may be
the caretaker, but --

00:13:01.982 --> 00:13:04.151 position:5% line:77% align:start
Wait, Lady Yuri!
Stop!
Let go!

00:13:04.184 --> 00:13:06.688 position:5% line:71% align:start
The kid did
the right thing!
Huh?

00:13:06.721 --> 00:13:08.255 position:27% line:89% align:start
He did the <i>what?</i>

00:13:08.289 --> 00:13:12.226 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's impossible to escape
from the White Steel Eel.

00:13:12.259 --> 00:13:15.963 position:5% line:83% align:start
So rather than flee, you have
no choice but to face it

00:13:15.996 --> 00:13:18.198 position:5% line:89% align:start
and leap into its mouth.

00:13:18.232 --> 00:13:19.601 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?!

00:13:19.634 --> 00:13:22.570 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:13:22.604 --> 00:13:24.972 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Grunts ]

00:13:25.005 --> 00:13:28.042 position:5% line:83% align:start
Overcoming the fear
of death

00:13:28.075 --> 00:13:31.412 position:5% line:83% align:start
is the true answer
to this test.

00:13:31.445 --> 00:13:36.116 position:10% line:83% align:start
He entered its mouth knowing
he would have stabbed the eel?

00:13:36.150 --> 00:13:37.752 position:24% line:83% align:start
If you already knew
the answer,

00:13:37.786 --> 00:13:39.219 position:30% line:83% align:start
why didn't you
just simply tell him?!

00:13:39.253 --> 00:13:41.255 position:13% line:83% align:start
Even if someone
already knows the answer,

00:13:41.288 --> 00:13:44.526 position:5% line:77% align:start
they usually aren't
able to do anything
so apparently ridiculous.

00:13:46.293 --> 00:13:47.595 position:5% line:89% align:start
That boy...

00:13:47.629 --> 00:13:51.332 position:5% line:83% align:start
he has something even stronger
than the fear of death.

00:13:51.365 --> 00:13:54.803 position:5% line:83% align:start
He has something that
allowed him to face that fear

00:13:54.835 --> 00:13:56.738 position:5% line:89% align:start
and conquer it forever.

00:13:56.771 --> 00:14:02.076 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:14:02.109 --> 00:14:03.077 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:14:03.110 --> 00:14:04.813 position:5% line:77% align:start
What the...?!
Headon!

00:14:04.845 --> 00:14:06.681 position:61% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:14:06.715 --> 00:14:09.551 position:50% line:83% align:start
The real test
hasn't even begun yet.

00:14:12.986 --> 00:14:14.888 position:27% line:89% align:start
What's going on?

00:14:14.922 --> 00:14:16.758 position:33% line:83% align:start
Why hasn't he
destroyed the ball?

00:14:16.791 --> 00:14:18.459 position:58% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid
I can't answer that.

00:14:18.492 --> 00:14:22.496 position:24% line:83% align:start
What? What are you
planning now, Caretaker?

00:14:22.530 --> 00:14:24.431 position:10% line:89% align:start
[ Bam grunts, metal scrapes ]

00:14:26.801 --> 00:14:28.202 position:41% line:89% align:start
Break!

00:14:29.704 --> 00:14:30.971 position:41% line:89% align:start
Break!

00:14:34.208 --> 00:14:36.176 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Grunting ]

00:14:38.546 --> 00:14:40.447 position:10% line:89% align:start
[ Rocks rumble, Bam shouts ]

00:14:47.221 --> 00:14:48.989 position:41% line:89% align:start
Break.

00:14:49.022 --> 00:14:50.991 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Echoing ] <i>Break!</i>

00:14:51.559 --> 00:14:53.260 position:24% line:89% align:start
[ Rocks crashing ]

00:14:53.293 --> 00:14:59.366 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:14:59.400 --> 00:15:03.103 position:5% line:83% align:start
What are you...what are you
doing down there?

00:15:03.971 --> 00:15:05.205 position:55% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:15:06.708 --> 00:15:09.209 position:27% line:83% align:start
Wait!
I'm coming for you.

00:15:10.310 --> 00:15:11.813 position:24% line:5% align:start
I see.

00:15:11.846 --> 00:15:14.114 position:5% line:5% align:start
So you don't remember
anything?

00:15:15.583 --> 00:15:17.084 position:7% line:89% align:start
I guess...

00:15:17.117 --> 00:15:19.219 position:5% line:89% align:start
that must be scary.

00:15:20.555 --> 00:15:23.290 position:7% line:83% align:start
But now it's okay.
You don't have to worry.

00:15:25.459 --> 00:15:27.227 position:7% line:89% align:start
I'm here with you.

00:15:27.261 --> 00:15:28.863 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:15:28.897 --> 00:15:30.197 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:15:30.230 --> 00:15:31.699 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:15:31.733 --> 00:15:33.167 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:15:34.468 --> 00:15:36.470 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:15:36.504 --> 00:15:37.505 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:15:37.539 --> 00:15:39.774 position:5% line:89% align:start
I want to see the stars.

00:15:39.808 --> 00:15:41.442 position:58% line:89% align:start
Stars?

00:15:41.475 --> 00:15:42.976 position:5% line:89% align:start
At the top of the tower,

00:15:43.010 --> 00:15:45.112 position:13% line:83% align:start
here's a thing
called the sky.

00:15:45.145 --> 00:15:47.314 position:10% line:83% align:start
It stretches out
forever and ever.

00:15:47.347 --> 00:15:51.385 position:5% line:83% align:start
They say it's full of countless
beautiful shining stars.

00:15:53.220 --> 00:15:55.989 position:5% line:83% align:start
Bam: Then they must be
just like you.

00:15:56.023 --> 00:15:57.892 position:55% line:83% align:start
[ Gasps ]
And where did you learn

00:15:57.926 --> 00:15:59.761 position:19% line:89% align:start
to say something like that?

00:15:59.794 --> 00:16:01.328 position:10% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps, laughs ]

00:16:01.361 --> 00:16:02.996 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:16:03.030 --> 00:16:05.265 position:30% line:89% align:start
Bam, I'm just so tired.

00:16:05.299 --> 00:16:07.802 position:30% line:83% align:start
Sick and tired of being
in this dark world.

00:16:07.836 --> 00:16:09.203 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:16:09.236 --> 00:16:10.605 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Break!</i>

00:16:10.638 --> 00:16:12.941 position:5% line:89% align:start
Rachel, don't leave me.

00:16:12.973 --> 00:16:15.442 position:33% line:89% align:start
Just breaaak!

00:16:19.112 --> 00:16:21.883 position:44% line:83% align:start
It appears he was
a bit too loud.

00:16:21.916 --> 00:16:23.050 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's not good.

00:16:23.083 --> 00:16:25.419 position:10% line:89% align:start
Run, newbie! Run!

00:16:25.452 --> 00:16:26.621 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Roars ]

00:16:26.654 --> 00:16:27.822 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yuri: Run!

00:16:27.856 --> 00:16:30.324 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hurry! Run!

00:16:31.391 --> 00:16:32.894 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey, newbie!

00:16:32.927 --> 00:16:35.830 position:7% line:83% align:start
Listen, you have to
talk to the Black March!

00:16:35.864 --> 00:16:37.765 position:19% line:83% align:start
Ask it for
its power -- <i>now!</i>

00:16:37.799 --> 00:16:39.032 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Gasps ]

00:16:40.969 --> 00:16:43.036 position:44% line:83% align:start
Evan, are you out
of your mind or what?!

00:16:43.070 --> 00:16:44.204 position:30% line:83% align:start
That sword won't listen
to <i>my</i> --

00:16:44.238 --> 00:16:46.574 position:7% line:83% align:start
Do what I tell you,
right now!

00:16:49.844 --> 00:16:51.779 position:19% line:89% align:start
Grant me your strength!

00:16:55.683 --> 00:16:57.384 position:35% line:89% align:start
I don't...

00:16:57.417 --> 00:16:58.452 position:61% line:89% align:start
Hmm.

00:16:58.485 --> 00:17:08.428 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:17:08.462 --> 00:17:10.230 position:27% line:89% align:start
Black March: Boy.

00:17:11.699 --> 00:17:16.136 position:13% line:83% align:start
You search for the strength
with which to climb the tower?

00:17:16.169 --> 00:17:17.572 position:7% line:89% align:start
Bam: No, actually.

00:17:17.605 --> 00:17:19.072 position:47% line:89% align:start
Hm?

00:17:19.106 --> 00:17:21.408 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm not interested
in climbing it.

00:17:21.441 --> 00:17:23.477 position:13% line:83% align:start
But I beg you,
please grant me your strength

00:17:23.511 --> 00:17:26.814 position:5% line:83% align:start
so that I may see Rachel
one more time.

00:17:26.848 --> 00:17:28.148 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Chuckles ]

00:17:28.181 --> 00:17:30.484 position:24% line:89% align:start
Such a boring boy.

00:17:31.019 --> 00:17:32.787 position:58% line:89% align:start
But...

00:17:34.989 --> 00:17:36.891 position:47% line:83% align:start
Since you have
such a divine face,

00:17:36.925 --> 00:17:39.827 position:44% line:83% align:start
I shall grant it,
just this once.

00:17:39.861 --> 00:17:41.295 position:33% line:89% align:start
She's not...

00:17:41.328 --> 00:17:42.496 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:17:42.530 --> 00:17:44.231 position:21% line:83% align:start
She never granted <i>me</i>
her strength,

00:17:44.264 --> 00:17:46.834 position:38% line:83% align:start
no matter
how many times I asked.

00:17:46.868 --> 00:17:49.336 position:13% line:89% align:start
Maybe she just prefers men?

00:17:49.369 --> 00:17:50.437 position:61% line:89% align:start
Correct.

00:17:50.470 --> 00:17:52.774 position:44% line:83% align:start
So now it's time
for you to go, woman.

00:17:52.807 --> 00:17:54.107 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hmph!

00:17:54.141 --> 00:17:57.045 position:5% line:83% align:start
So the legend of the tower
is real after all.

00:17:57.077 --> 00:17:58.245 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's not fair.

00:17:58.278 --> 00:18:00.347 position:24% line:89% align:start
I won't accept it!

00:18:00.380 --> 00:18:06.788 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:06.821 --> 00:18:08.523 position:13% line:89% align:start
What the hell?

00:18:08.556 --> 00:18:12.894 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:12.927 --> 00:18:13.928 position:38% line:89% align:start
[ Roars ]

00:18:13.962 --> 00:18:16.531 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Rumbling ]

00:18:16.564 --> 00:18:18.432 position:44% line:83% align:start
What?
What happened just now?

00:18:18.465 --> 00:18:21.869 position:64% line:83% align:start
You mean
you don't know?

00:18:21.903 --> 00:18:24.539 position:47% line:83% align:start
He has ascended
to the next level.

00:18:24.572 --> 00:18:26.574 position:5% line:83% align:start
Okay, fine, terrific.
So now what?!

00:18:26.608 --> 00:18:28.475 position:5% line:83% align:start
He still has the Black March,
and that's not good.

00:18:28.509 --> 00:18:30.011 position:10% line:83% align:start
What are we
supposed to do?

00:18:30.044 --> 00:18:31.913 position:10% line:83% align:start
We just have to get it back,
that's all.

00:18:31.946 --> 00:18:33.548 position:72% line:77% align:start
Huh?
We're going after him.

00:18:33.581 --> 00:18:34.916 position:52% line:83% align:start
Whoa, whoa.
Hang on a second.

00:18:34.949 --> 00:18:36.316 position:30% line:83% align:start
We're forbidden
from entering

00:18:36.350 --> 00:18:37.819 position:24% line:83% align:start
the testing grounds
for climbing the tower!

00:18:37.852 --> 00:18:41.623 position:5% line:83% align:start
Get moving! A life where nothing
interesting ever happens

00:18:41.656 --> 00:18:43.024 position:24% line:89% align:start
isn't worth a shit.

00:18:43.057 --> 00:18:44.291 position:5% line:77% align:start
[ Groans ]
Well, Guide?

00:18:44.324 --> 00:18:46.094 position:33% line:83% align:start
What are you
standing around for?

00:18:46.126 --> 00:18:47.629 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hey! Wait!

00:18:47.662 --> 00:18:49.296 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ Muttering ]
She's the most stubborn...

00:18:49.329 --> 00:18:52.567 position:13% line:83% align:start
Headon: What a fascinating
gathering this has been.

00:18:52.600 --> 00:18:59.841 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:18:59.874 --> 00:19:07.048 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:07.081 --> 00:19:09.984 position:16% line:83% align:start
I look forward to seeing
what happens next.

00:19:10.018 --> 00:19:11.786 position:27% line:89% align:start
Very intriguing.

00:19:14.622 --> 00:19:17.491 position:21% line:83% align:start
Black March: Even if
the two of you are reunited,

00:19:17.525 --> 00:19:20.928 position:21% line:83% align:start
things will never be
exactly as they once were.

00:19:20.962 --> 00:19:22.462 position:16% line:89% align:start
When you meet her again,

00:19:22.496 --> 00:19:26.067 position:24% line:83% align:start
she will have lived
for some time without you.

00:19:26.100 --> 00:19:28.335 position:27% line:89% align:start
But first, sleep.

00:19:28.368 --> 00:19:31.471 position:30% line:83% align:start
The road ahead
is fraught with danger.

00:19:31.506 --> 00:19:41.281 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:41.314 --> 00:19:44.484 position:27% line:5% align:start
[ Wind rushing ]

00:19:44.519 --> 00:19:48.690 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:48.723 --> 00:19:49.891 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ Groans ]

00:19:49.924 --> 00:19:56.764 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:19:56.798 --> 00:20:03.171 position:64% line:5% align:start
♪♪

00:20:03.203 --> 00:20:04.404 position:33% line:89% align:start
[ Coughing ]

00:20:04.438 --> 00:20:06.140 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>-Uh...testing?</i>
-Huh?

00:20:06.174 --> 00:20:09.242 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Testing, 1, 2, 3.</i>
 <i>Testing.</i>

00:20:10.210 --> 00:20:11.713 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Hello, regulars,</i>

00:20:11.746 --> 00:20:14.549 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>and welcome to</i>
 <i>the second floor of the tower.</i>

